			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Peggy									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>My absolute favorite veggie broth is Imagine Organic Vegetarian No-Chicken Broth.  It has the lightness of chicken broth, but without the chicken!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2019-01-29T17:17:09-05:00 class="comment-time">
