				<b class="fn author-name">
											Deanna									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Hello Friday night dinner! This will go perfectly with my recent tahini obsession. It started with your butternut squash and garbanzo bean salad, now I just put tahini dressing on everything.</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
