					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816368#respond" data-commentid="816368" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816368" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Deanna" aria-label="Reply to Deanna">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
