											<a href="http://imiksimik.wordpress.com">Anny</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Perfect timing! Was just trying to dream up something tasty but meal-worthy I can toss together for a friend coming in from the Middle East tonight.</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-24T12:37:50-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816371">
						<span class="date">March 24, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">12:37 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816371#respond" data-commentid="816371" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816371" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anny" aria-label="Reply to Anny">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
