	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-816372">
		<article id="div-comment-816372" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Carly									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Just this morning, I thought to myself, &#8220;why do I have so many bags of chickpeas and when will I even finish them?&#8221;  Question asked and answered in a few hours.  Brilliant.</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-24T12:38:21-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816372">
						<span class="date">March 24, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">12:38 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816372#respond" data-commentid="816372" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816372" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Carly" aria-label="Reply to Carly">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

