			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Beth Cook									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>I&#8217;m trying to broaden my eating horizons.  I do not usually like chickpeas but I really want to so I&#8217;m going to try this!  I&#8217;ll let you know how it goes.</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-24T12:39:26-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816373">
