					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816373#respond" data-commentid="816373" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816373" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Beth Cook" aria-label="Reply to Beth Cook">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
