	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-816374">
		<article id="div-comment-816374" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											<a href="https://ausplendor.wordpress.com">ausplendor</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>YAAS MIDDLE EASTERN NACHOS. This leads to a whole host of great ideas. MIDDLE EASTERN 7 LAYER DIP???</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-24T12:40:07-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816374">
						<span class="date">March 24, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">12:40 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816374#respond" data-commentid="816374" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816374" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to ausplendor" aria-label="Reply to ausplendor">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

		</article><!-- #comment-816374 -->
	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-816375">
		<article id="div-comment-816375" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Amy									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>This recipe looks fantastic, and I cannot wait to make it for my family.  Question, though:  I always rinse and drain canned chickpeas.  Is 3/4 cup veggie broth enough if they are rinsed and drained, or should I skip my usual step?  Thank you!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-24T12:47:43-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816375">
						<span class="date">March 24, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">12:47 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816375#respond" data-commentid="816375" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816375" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Amy" aria-label="Reply to Amy">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

		</article><!-- #comment-816375 -->
	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-816376">
