			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Dina									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>This looks crazy good. Any suggestions for someone who is allergic to nuts (pine nuts included)?</p>
