											<a href="http://theprestigiousschool.com">The Prestigious School</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>This looks so good! I&#8217;m going to try putting the beans in the slow cooker before work. Unless I sleep too late&#8230;</p>
			</div>

