				<b class="fn author-name">
											Michelle S									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>This looks brilliant! I&#8217;ll definitely be making it this week!</p>
<p>I don&#8217;t have a Dutch oven; do you suppose for the baking part, I could improvise with a foil packet in a baking dish or something?</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-24T14:24:51-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816400">
						<span class="date">March 24, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">2:24 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
