				<b class="fn author-name">
											Michelle S									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Just saw the slow-cooker comments; never mind, I&#8217;ll try that!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-24T14:31:45-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816401">
						<span class="date">March 24, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">2:31 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
