			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>I had just planned on making your carrot salad with tahini and crisped chickpeas this week and now think I will add a dash of paprika to the chickpeas a la desertcandy.  Have you ever tried asian sesame paste in lieu of tahini?  I love the toasted taste.</p>
