				<b class="fn author-name">
											<a href="http://prairiekuchen.com">Jodi@prairiekuchen</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>This looks so good! I just bought a bag of dried chick peas yesterday &#8211; when I got home to unpack &#8211; I thought, &#8220;What in the world was I thinking?&#8221;<br />
Apparently Baked Chick Peas with Yogurt! Thanks!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-25T08:22:08-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816446">
						<span class="date">March 25, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">8:22 am</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816446#respond" data-commentid="816446" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816446" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Jodi@prairiekuchen" aria-label="Reply to Jodi@prairiekuchen">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
