									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>ooooh, I love this recipe!!  I have a thing for chickpeas!  Also loving all the beautiful veges going with them in this dish!!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-25T09:23:06-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816451">
						<span class="date">March 25, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">9:23 am</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816451#respond" data-commentid="816451" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816451" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Deborah @ The Harvest Kitchen" aria-label="Reply to Deborah @ The Harvest Kitchen">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

		</article><!-- #comment-816451 -->
	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-816452">
		<article id="div-comment-816452" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Kathleen									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Oh this makes me sooooo happy!  As a vegan, and dying for some warmer spring, the timing of this could not be better.  My inspiration has waned and now it&#8217;s back!  Thanks so much.</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-25T09:28:36-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816452">
						<span class="date">March 25, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">9:28 am</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816452#respond" data-commentid="816452" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816452" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Kathleen" aria-label="Reply to Kathleen">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
