	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-816453">
		<article id="div-comment-816453" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											christi in ma									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>I think this will be a perfect Friday Lent supper idea. And easy to make at the end of a long week! Thanks Deb!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-25T09:58:23-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816453">
						<span class="date">March 25, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">9:58 am</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816453#respond" data-commentid="816453" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816453" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to christi in ma" aria-label="Reply to christi in ma">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

		</article><!-- #comment-816453 -->
	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-816454">
		<article id="div-comment-816454" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											<a href="http://www.asianinamericamag.com">Betty Ann Quirino @Mango_Queen</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>This is a great way to cook with chickpeas or garbanzos as I call it sometimes. I often use it as a condiment to casseroles or stews, but to make it the star ingredient looks delightful like you did here. Thanks for sharing this recipe of Baked Chickpeas with pita chips and yogurt, Deb. Happy Spring!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-25T10:06:53-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816454">
						<span class="date">March 25, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">10:06 am</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816454#respond" data-commentid="816454" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816454" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Betty Ann Quirino @Mango_Queen" aria-label="Reply to Betty Ann Quirino @Mango_Queen">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

		</article><!-- #comment-816454 -->
	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
