	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-816457">
		<article id="div-comment-816457" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Amanda									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>I made this last night and it was awesome! Folded in some sauteed Kale (one of those bags of Tuscan Kale from Trader Joe&#8217;s) towards the end of the cooking process and it was great. Equally great with just the chickpea element and a poached egg for breakfast.</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-25T11:29:56-05:00 class="comment-time">
