				<b class="fn author-name">
											<a href="http://www.littlehousepantry.com">sarah | little house pantry</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>How much of this can be make ahead? It looks delicious but multi-step. I&#8217;m imagining making it for guests but not wanting to be cooking right up until we eat.</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-25T12:13:22-05:00 class="comment-time">
