					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816460#respond" data-commentid="816460" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816460" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Sonia" aria-label="Reply to Sonia">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

		</article><!-- #comment-816460 -->
	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-816461">
