			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											<a href="http://fromjessicaskitchen.com/black-bottom-oatmeal-pie-for-pi-day/">Jessica | From Jessica&#8217;s Kitchen</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>This looks like some delicious comfort food and would go so well with coconut yogurt and gluten free tortilla and love that your chickpea recipe is already gluten and dairy free! :)</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-25T13:35:12-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816461">
						<span class="date">March 25, 2015</span>
