	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-816477">
		<article id="div-comment-816477" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											<a href="http://www.mateamilojkovic.com/">Matea</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>I have such a hard time saving the chickpeas and not eating them all once they&#8217;re cooked! Love it! :)</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-03-26T08:32:06-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816477">
						<span class="date">March 26, 2015</span>
