			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Sandra									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Thank you! Thank you! Thank you! This was frickin awesome! Sooo loving that I have leftovers for tonight too!  :)</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2015-04-06T17:22:31-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-816534">
						<span class="date">April 6, 2015</span>
						at						<span class="time">5:22 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=816534#respond" data-commentid="816534" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-816534" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Sandra" aria-label="Reply to Sandra">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
