			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Beth Handa									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Where do you buy your Rancho Gordo beans?</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2018-03-12T08:08:00-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-1037465">
						<span class="date">March 12, 2018</span>
						at						<span class="time">8:08 am</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=1037465#respond" data-commentid="1037465" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-1037465" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Beth Handa" aria-label="Reply to Beth Handa">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
