		</article><!-- #comment-1037465 -->
	 </li>
	<ol class="children">
	<li class="comment byuser comment-author-debsk bypostauthor odd alt depth-2" id="comment-1037915">
		<article id="div-comment-1037915" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											<a href="http://smittenkitchen.com">deb</a>
									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>I order them <a href="https://www.ranchogordo.com/collections/heirloom-beans" rel="nofollow">online</a>, usually. Maybe once a year or so, loading up on what I think I&#8217;ll need.</p>
