	<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1 i-made-this" id="comment-2001112">
		<article id="div-comment-2001112" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Suzy									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>This was absolutely perfect.  So flavorful, and I don&#8217;t think I&#8217;ve been this satisfied after a meal in a long time.  I used pita chips from a bag, because it&#8217;s Tuesday, and it the right choice.  Thank you for this recipe!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2021-03-30T17:57:51-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-2001112">
						<span class="date">March 30, 2021</span>
						at						<span class="time">5:57 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=2001112#respond" data-commentid="2001112" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-2001112" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Suzy" aria-label="Reply to Suzy">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

		</article><!-- #comment-2001112 -->
	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 i-made-this" id="comment-2082972">
		<article id="div-comment-2082972" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Mary									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>I&#8217;ve been making and loving this recipe for a long now, but tonight was the first time I cooked the beans in the instant pot.. I wanted to share that it turned out great! I only had 2ish hours to soak the beans, cooked them under pressure for 42 minutes, let pressure release naturally for 15 minutes, and then manually released for the rest. They were perfect!</p>
<p>Thanks for the great recipe!!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2021-05-26T20:33:47-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-2082972">
						<span class="date">May 26, 2021</span>
						at						<span class="time">8:33 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=2082972#respond" data-commentid="2082972" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-2082972" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Mary" aria-label="Reply to Mary">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

		</article><!-- #comment-2082972 -->
	 </li>
	</li><!-- #comment-## -->
	<li class="comment even thread-even depth-1 i-made-this" id="comment-2473131">
		<article id="div-comment-2473131" class="comment-body">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<b class="fn author-name">
											Gretchen									</b>
			</div><!-- .vcard -->

			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>Served this to my skeptical children last night and they LOVED IT &#8211; a total winner. Thank you!</p>
			</div>

			<footer class="comment-footer comment-metadata">
				<time 2022-01-07T15:44:27-05:00 class="comment-time">
					<a href=" https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/#comment-2473131">
						<span class="date">January 7, 2022</span>
						at						<span class="time">3:44 pm</span>
					</a>
				</time>

				<span class="edit-link">
									</span>

				<span class="reply-link">
					<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://smittenkitchen.com/2015/03/baked-chickpeas-with-pita-chips-and-yogurt/?replytocom=2473131#respond" data-commentid="2473131" data-postid="14933" data-belowelement="comment-2473131" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Gretchen" aria-label="Reply to Gretchen">Reply</a>				</span><!-- .reply -->
			</footer><!-- .comment-footer -->

